OL,3,CWhistleblower reveals how health
OL,4,Cauthorities left him devastated
OL,6,FA senior consultant who turned
OL,7,Fwhistleblower to expose the cervical
OL,8,Fscreening scandal in the Southern
OL,9,FHealth and Social Care Trust has told
OL,10,FUTV he felt questioned when he raised
OL,11,Fhis concerns.
OL,13,FMichael McKenna decided to speak to
OL,14,FUTV about his experience as a
OL,15,Fwhistleblower after the health
OL,16,Fminister encouraged medics to speak
OL,17,Fout in the wake of a damning report
OL,18,Finto poor behaviour and culture within
OL,19,Fthe Belfast Trust's Cardiac Surgery
OL,20,FUnit.
