OL,3,CWhistleblower reveals how health
OL,4,Cauthorities left him devastated
OL,6,FIn the first of a two part interview
OL,7,Fwith Dr McKenna, the consultant
OL,8,Fpathologist, who has more than 15
OL,9,Fyears experience, said more needs to
OL,10,Fbe done to protect whistleblowers in
OL,11,Fthe health service.
OL,13,FDr McKenna said he flagged critical
OL,14,Fissues in the cervical screening
OL,15,Fprogramme within the Southern Health
OL,16,FTrust back in October 2021.
