OL,3,CWhistleblower reveals how health
OL,4,Cauthorities left him devastated
OL,6,FHe told UTV that he was brought to "a
OL,7,Fvery dark place".
OL,9,FDr McKenna told UTV that he was
OL,10,Fcompelled to speak out after Health
OL,11,FMinister Mike Nesbitt asked to hear
OL,12,Fpeople's experiences which served as a
OL,13,F"very powerful motivator".
OL,15,FWhen asked if he was worried about the
OL,16,Freaction he might get, the consultant
OL,17,Fsaid he was "doing what the minister
OL,18,Fasked".
