OL,6,F"Raising concerns and being open and
OL,7,Ftransparent is the value of the health
OL,8,Fservice."
OL,10,FIn a statement the Public Health
OL,11,FAgency said it "understands that the
OL,12,Fpoints that have been made around the
OL,13,Fhandling of raised concerns and
OL,14,Fwhistleblowing are the subject of an
OL,15,Fongoing process being managed by the
OL,16,FSouthern Trust in line with HSC policy.
OL,18,F"This has not yet been concluded, it
OL,19,Fwould not be appropriate for the
OL,20,Fagency to comment at this stage."
