OL,6,FThe PHA said it "encourages any staff
OL,7,Fmember with concerns about any element
OL,8,Fof patient care to raise these with
OL,9,Ftheir employer".
OL,11,FThe Southern Health Trust added: "We
OL,12,Fstrongly encourage all our staff to
OL,13,Fmake senior leaders aware of any
OL,14,Fissues giving them concern.
