OL,6,F"Dr McKenna has brought a number of
OL,7,Fimportant issues to our attention, and
OL,8,Fas a result the trust and this staff
OL,9,Fmember have been engaged in open
OL,10,Fdialogue regarding these where the
OL,11,Ffocus from the Trust's perspective has
OL,12,Fbeen on resolution, understanding,
OL,13,Flearning and improvement.
OL,15,F"We are fully committed to having a
OL,16,Fworking environment where staff are
OL,17,Fsupported not penalised or feel
OL,18,Fpunished for raising concerns with us,
OL,19,Fand one in which we seek to resolve
OL,20,Fany concerns to avoid detriment where
OL,21,Fappropriate and necessary.
