OL,4,Cauthorities left him devastated
OL,6,F"We continue to engage with Dr McKenna
OL,7,Fas part of this ongoing process with a
OL,8,Ffurther follow up meeting to take
OL,9,Fplace before the end of June."
OL,11,FDr McKenna's concerns come at the same
OL,12,Ftime as a group of health staff in the
OL,13,FBelfast Health and Social Care Trust
OL,14,Fshared their "serious and sustained
OL,15,Fconcerns" regarding the leadership and
OL,16,Fmanagement at the trust with members
OL,17,Fof Stormont's Health Committee.
