OL,3,CWhistleblower reveals how health
OL,4,Cauthorities left him devastated
OL,6,FIn a letter to members, seen by UTV,
OL,7,Fthe group said it wanted to
OL,8,F"...express serious and sustained
OL,9,Fconcerns regarding the leadership,
OL,10,Fclinical oversight and governance
OL,11,Fwithin the Belfast Health and Social
OL,12,FCare Trust."
OL,14,FDr Chris Hagan, a medical director at
OL,15,Fthe Belfast Trust told the health
OL,16,Fcommittee that he found it "upsetting"
OL,17,Fwhen he read the letter.
OL,19,F"I don't think it reflects my
OL,20,Fexperience working in an organisation
OL,21,Fthat I have worked in since 1998."
